sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    User ->> AuthenticationController: POST /api/v1/auth/mfa/verify
    AuthenticationController ->> AuthRequestContext: fromHttpRequest(request, deviceId)
    AuthenticationController ->> AuthCommonServices: completeMfaChallengeLogin(challengeId, code, providerType, response, context)
    AuthCommonServices -->> AuthenticationController: completion
    AuthenticationController -->> User: 200 ApiResponse {message: "mfa verification successful"}
